data.description: This beautiful and roomy ranch is situated on a residential lot close to Adams State College, Alamosa schools, restaurants, trendy coffee shops, entertainment, outdoor spaces, and The Rio Grande River. This property has a beautiful front yard with nice mature trees.  Upon entering the house you will find an inviting floor plan with a Huge living room leading into a modern sizable kitchen boasting stainless appliances with plenty of cabinet space.  The home boasts 4 generously sized bedrooms and 2.5 baths. There is a large primary bedroom with a big closet and a full primary bathroom that includes a double vanity, and plenty of storage. Another large secondary primary bedroom has 2 closets and a 1/2 bath attached. The other 2 bedrooms have large closets and there is also a large main bathroom. The back of the house has a spacious separate laundry room including washer and dryer, and mud room where you exit into the 2 car garage. The fenced in back yard has a covered patio- ideal for grilling and summer time eating,  2 storage sheds, and mature trees. So many accents in and out come see all the details that make this home so special!
